name: The Angie Files - Episode 3 - "Dear, Dear, Bread & Beer"
description: This week, Angie had a biopsy and found out she has skin cancer on her face.  It should be easy to remove. She has been sleeping 16-20 hours a day since Copper left us. She's been pretty down, although this morning she was unusually excited as she recited her favorite poem while holding 2 aubergines cuz we all made it thru the exploit.  I don't know where she picked this saying up, but I've heard this all my life, although as far as H=N is concerned, I’d be HERE regardless. "Dear, Dear, Bread and Beer, If I had a million, I wouldn't be here"
